{"id":606526,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC82MDY1MjY=","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/606526","title":"[tianma-static] Security issue with XSS.","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2019-06-11T16:08:58.926Z","submitted_at":"2019-06-11T16:08:58.926Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"wooeong22","url":"/wooeong22","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/492/499/1053b26b6f2e620ae20c28e0b62b85836fee2d73_original.png/235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":false,"verified":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":23949,"url":"https://hackerone.com/nodejs-ecosystem","handle":"nodejs-ecosystem","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/023/949/3ea3b2ae039a8f955a4a8fe65d99fe85dc817398_original./3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"disabled","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"Node.js third-party modules","twitter_handle":"","website":"https://nodejs.org/en/security/","about":"This program was used to handle vulnerabilities in the Node.js ecosystem."}},"has_bounty?":false,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":["CVE-2018-16474"],"singular_disclosure_disabled":false,"disclosed_at":"2020-10-12T20:44:40.207Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2020-09-12T20:44:16.714Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"I would like to report XSS in tianma-static\nIt allows XSS and HTML Injection\n\nFirst of all, It is my first report and I am sorry that I am not good at English T.T \nthank you.\n\n# Module\n\n**module name:** tianma-static\n**version:** 1.0.4\n**npm page:** `https://www.npmjs.com/package/tianma-static`\n\n## Module Description\n\n\u003e Provide a static file service.\n\n# Vulnerability\n\n## Vulnerability Description\n\n1) File content type\nwhen I look a CVE-2018-16474([CVE-2018-16474](https://www.cvedetails.com/cve/CVE-2018-16474/), #403692), I think that's vulnerability need arbitrary file(name) upload.\n\nIf upload is possible, Attacker can upload `html` file. Also content type of the response header becomes `text/html` and it is possible to Stored XSS.\n\n{F506823}\n\n2) HTML Injection (It can lead to reflected XSS)\nwhen a send `%2f` in path (example: http://127.0.0.1:8080/%2f), `resolve` function make a normal path on the filesystem. but `req.pathname` will print out a manipulated path.\n\nso I can insert any html.\n\n{F506824}\n\nReflected XSS using HTML only is not easy bypass the modern browser.\nbut if I can upload any file, Reflected XSS is possible Using load script.\n\n{F506825}\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n\n1) File content type\n\u003e - upload html file with XSS script. \n\u003e - xss fired\n\n2) HTML Injection (reflected XSS)\n\u003e - upload any file with XSS script.\n\u003e - access `/%2f\u003cscript src='/[filename]'\u003e\u003c/script\u003e`\n\u003e - xss fired\n\n## Patch\n\n1. add content type header in response. \n2. change `decodeURI` to `decodeURIComponent`. or denied malicious path.\n\n# Wrap up\n- I contacted the maintainer to let them know: N\n- I opened an issue in the related repository: N\n\n## Impact\n\nIf file upload is possible, XSS can occur.","weakness":{"id":62,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Stored"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":506823,"file_name":"1._html_File_Stored_XSS.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/506/823/2b21833d6357577c47f97f734ae497ef8fda52b6/1._html_File_Stored_XSS.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%221._html_File_Stored_XSS.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%271._html_File_Stored_XSS.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQVNLSD7KF%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T084421Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQC5FZYMlS628CuhZFIJ1HEIqBwicJ6%2F9T9I9aZbSbFgmgIhAJ26eDcBc%2FGOufGkolfwBYzM2AL8tenUBQZa3nypwcrYKrsFCPH%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgzmyPwoXegWzTVOZxUqjwV1tzF63HAWxG%2BJKbAXG6OMhV0ZEI%2FBWvCmPTjsJtzW6jVBf9zAJbEcswkXX%2FBooJBJjGjDO475kShGTOklWZ0h7A4HO61fFj%2BHCHd0Z7A%2FZRgS5ybfkHTv9ASDt66EK%2FqXjXnIdbKNl8uT2X5zlteCJz1VKn1tMsF493dVHnqakDr7%2BY%2BckcsIParimJPwWwbhRNawxqM2h7BCoyGIE2sifVKcN5NFNnSowlzGHdaC084eM6jIK0IiZTq1EbcVD%2F9eg0XWtO%2B%2FMCr%2Bjbmy0S3LkpbcyC47Rscb2LqeIQkz1DqnZed3Q7DaaYWqWEb8k%2Bd5Gb3FTOl%2F%2F4EBlVTdsiLIrgp%2FEA7ImgUfdQocm%2FadpNAPnQJIQ0bbJbzTUtoatTC7kTy8%2Bdm0Ilh%2BrHkWZUSIBcJ2yNUkJSNQsluF9x%2BbyAZWrqz31rfXXXLlB20VHtzAsVW68GMX8SYH756IFpnQiarlKJSL7gpirSlrz2KgVKZsVx%2F0dmlg8obJymx603RTjl14H9XB4UxK8pqIMRE82H1otZ%2F3Jr4SavIRmY8jMa2V%2FxyZ8g1iJKmga0jhoCQ%2BSmzKgpRl7%2BptlILw53GrVLGB1KHhy4SZxSdImqD71oK0cm7EQM1MjeCc5Slk8NwgSW5GmsMiFt6FOPkDRWcakJpQusJ%2BwHGUzSpnNsYuKNHjnLnuDoS5yY3Hy1swfBMy42EPkEmqUMFYFTx3BxW1S6Ox%2BZPY2meonZGqQj2fqF9FRacP708fABAPnxjZtOmF7YJhLBKQIbzY5dho3vxRE5Wyl%2FMlikH8%2BD3D079nUTktQtNFNK38s5e